name: MyList
0:
”Alexa open My List”
”Please add getting groceries to my list”
”Alexa ask my list to delete the last item from it”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my list
des:
MyList is a streamlined text-based list that allows the management and retrieval of information on your Alexa whether it be a reminder to buy groceries or a memo to yourself. This skill simplifies the way people save information that's on their mind. There's no need to waste space in your mind on something you can just have Alexa save for you. Enjoy!

Credit for Skill icon: Free Vector Graphics by Vecteezy.com.

NOTICE: You cannot access lists on separate Echo devices.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
